{"type": "article", "id": 4657, "title": "Nendo Fuse & Cufflinks 系列衬衣", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-24T07:32:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233436SkvjHPZBcQ03Ex4Y.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 又将自己的设计拓展至了衬衫领域。这一次，设计团队带来<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/release/2014/\" target=\"_blank\">「Fuse」与「 Cufflinks」两个系列</a>共 9 种款型的衬衣。Fuse 系列的 5 件男士衬衣分为 Tie（在领口处设计了一条同色系假领带）、Layer（领口部分做成适合搭配毛衣穿着的圆弧样式）、Glasses（在口袋内缝入了一块眼镜清洁布）、Ruler （暗色量尺花纹）以及 Graph （网格状花纹）5 款。而 Cufflinks 女士系列则是围绕纽扣来做文章，4 款不同的衬衣 Half、Side、Wave 以及 Collar 分别在门襟、领口、下摆与袖口等细节处通过纽扣设计出不同的廓形。这两个系列的衬衣均在日本西武百货有售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233432HXGbkudFYKsMZypA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233432pBJVTAh5a9olzeOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233433eH1Iz4LuEsxfV9lg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233433jdLiFtVYyS2QCkc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233434tIzKX3vNlixGsHJr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233434UgA3zODBw0se8o6h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233434JdoYr3s5TIcWZPvC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233435K2lyx0XpH6EtWPi5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}